#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:724
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1636
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1671
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1732
